{"word":"G404 - ἀναψύχω - anapsýchō - an-aps-oo'-kho - Refresh","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναψύχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anapsýchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-aps-oo'-kho</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Refresh</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இளைப்பாறு"},{"paragraph":"to cool again, to cool off, recover from the effects of heat"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G5594 - ψύχω - psýchō - psoo'-kho/5594\">G5594</a>; properly to <i>cool off</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>relieve:</i> - refresh.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1374/1374\">G1374</a>, <a href=\"#/G3642/3642\">G3642</a>, <a href=\"#/G403/403\">G403</a>, <a href=\"#/G404/404\">G404</a>, <a href=\"#/G5590/5590\">G5590</a>, <a href=\"#/G5591/5591\">G5591</a>"}]}